#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer is an application for <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/TNEF\">TNEF</ulink> mail attachments."
msgstr ""
"Pregledovalnik datotek TNEF je aplikacija za <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/TNEF\">TNEF</ulink> poštne priponke."

#. Tag: keyword
