#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer allows to handle easily mail attachments using the TNEF "
"format. Those attachments are usually found in mails coming from <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> mail servers and embed the mail "
"properties as well as the actual attachments."
msgstr ""
"Pregledovalnik datotek TNEF omogoča enostavno obdelavo priponk pošte v "
"formatu TNEF. Te priponke so običajno v pošti, ki prihaja iz <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">Microsoftovih</trademark> poštnih strežnikov in vsebuje "
"lastnosti pošte ter dejanske priponke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An attachment in TNEF format is most often named <filename>winmail.dat</"
"filename> or <filename>win.dat</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Priponka v formatu TNEF se najpogosteje imenuje <filename>winmail.dat</"
"filename> ali <filename>win.dat</filename>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>TNEF Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavno okno TNEF</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>TNEF Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavno okno TNEF</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This utility program allows to perform various operations on those "
"attachments:"
msgstr ""
"Ta uporabniški program omogoča izvajanje različnih operacij na teh priponkah:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "View/open attachments with associated applications."
msgstr "Ogled/odpiranje priponk s povezanimi aplikacijami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extract actual attachments"
msgstr "Izvleci dejanske priponke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "View message properties (TNEF/MAPI)"
msgstr "Prikaz lastnosti sporočila (TNEF/MAPI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "View/extract message formatted text (in RTF format)"
msgstr "Ogled/izvleček oblikovanega besedila sporočila (v formatu RTF)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; automatically shows the content of a TNEF attachment. You can open "
"or save the attachments using the actions in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; samodejno prikaže vsebino priponke TNEF. Priponke lahko odprete ali "
"shranite z dejanji v kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>TNEF attachment in &kmail;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>TNEF priponka v &kmail;-u</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>TNEF attachment in &kmail;</phrase>"
